==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Tom o Bedlam
<hw>Tom o' Bed"lam</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <def>Formerly, a wandering
mendicant discharged as incurable from Bethlehem Hospital, England;
hence, a wandering mendicant, either mad or feigning to be so; a madman;
a bedlamite.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tomopteris</ent>⟦br⟧
